OL,3,CHealth minister to seek introduction
OL,4,Cof minimum alcohol pricing in NI
OL,6,FStormont's Health minister is to seek
OL,7,FExecutive approval for introducing
OL,8,Fminimum unit pricing for alcohol in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,11,FMike Nesbitt signalled his intention
OL,12,Fto implement a policy similar to that
OL,13,Fin operation in Scotland.
OL,15,FThe Scottish government set a Minimum
OL,16,FUnit Pricing (MUP) of 50p per unit of
OL,17,Falcohol when it introduced the measure
OL,18,Fin 2018. That price has recently been
OL,19,Fraised to 65p.
