OL,3,CHealth minister to seek introduction
OL,4,Cof minimum alcohol pricing in NI
OL,6,FMr Nesbitt said he wanted to work with
OL,7,Ffellow MLAs at Stormont to determine a
OL,8,Fsuitable minimum price in Northern
OL,9,FIreland.
OL,11,FHe outlined his intentions as he gave
OL,12,Fevidence to his Assembly scrutiny
OL,13,Fcommittee on Thursday afternoon.
OL,15,FThe Ulster Unionist Party leader said
OL,16,Fthe policy aligned with his "passion"
OL,17,Ffor addressing health inequalities.
