OL,3,CHealth minister to seek introduction
OL,4,Cof minimum alcohol pricing in NI
OL,6,F"I have asked officials to progress
OL,7,Fwork on the introduction of minimum
OL,8,Funit pricing for alcohol, something I
OL,9,Fwould like to achieve in this
OL,10,Fmandate," he said.
OL,12,F"And to my mind, this would complement
OL,13,Fthe Tobacco and Vaping Bill that is
OL,14,Fabout to go through Westminster. Both
OL,15,Fcan be key contributors to tackling
OL,16,Fhealth inequalities.
OL,18,F"Alcohol pricing can only progress
OL,19,Fwith Executive approval and I'll
OL,20,Fengage ministerial colleagues in due
OL,21,Fcourse.
