OL,3,CHealth minister to seek introduction
OL,4,Cof minimum alcohol pricing in NI
OL,6,F"If Executive approval is forthcoming,
OL,7,FI would like to work with (the)
OL,8,Fcommittee ` and in particular I would
OL,9,Fwelcome your advice on where to fix
OL,10,Fany minimum price.
OL,12,F"It could be 50p, it could be 55p, it
OL,13,Fmight be somewhere else."
OL,15,FThe minister's department undertook a
OL,16,Fpublic consultation exercise on
OL,17,Fsetting a minimum price for alcohol in
OL,18,F2022.
