OL,3,CHealth minister to seek introduction
OL,4,Cof minimum alcohol pricing in NI
OL,6,FMr Nesbitt told the committee that
OL,7,Falcohol misuse costs Northern Ireland
OL,8,F#900million a year.
OL,10,F"And that's never mind the devastating
OL,11,Fimpact on individuals, families and
OL,12,Fcommunities and indeed the stress on
OL,13,Four health service," he added.
OL,15,F"In 2022, 356 people here died from
OL,16,Falcohol-specific causes ` and that is
OL,17,Fthe highest total on record.
OL,19,F"In terms of health inequalities
OL,20,Fdeaths are up to five times higher in
OL,21,Fthe most deprived areas."
